# <type>(<scope>): <subject>   (≤72 字符,祈使句,不以句号结尾)
#
# <正文:改了什么、为什么;72~100 列换行>
#
# <footer:Rawf: <yyyy-mm-dd>/<task-slug> / Refs: <权威文档> /
#         Co-Authored-By: ... / BREAKING CHANGE: ...(或 type 后加 !)>
#
# types:  feat fix docs refactor perf test build ci chore style revert
# scopes: 可选,小写短词,按项目约定(如 web server deploy docs repo)
# 规范:   AGENTS.md「Git 提交规范」;由 .githooks/commit-msg 本地强制
# 启用:   git config core.hooksPath .githooks
#         git config commit.template .gitmessage
